snippet.title: Amber Heard talks about relatiohship with Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Hollywood actress Amber Heard has made a rare comment about her relationship with Johnny Depp, saying the two are determined to keep their romance out of the tabloids. In an exclusive interview with Flare magazine, it was revealed that the two will never be seen in public together, with the exception of their promotional duties for 'The Lone Ranger'.
